{"tid":1989451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［養龜撚入］緊急 我老母係馬路執左隻龜返屋企","createTime":"2020-04-26T03:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T02:18:10.000Z","uid":20834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce95d43f6a46ac2e95bcd57f1421bc17afff439b","tid":1989451,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"話說我老母係馬路見到隻龜<br />\n驚佢比車轆死<br />\n就執左返屋企<br />\n而家諗住放生 <br />\n<br />\n有冇手足知佢咩品種？<br />\n放生應該放去邊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MPyM5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3MPyM5x.jpg&h=b1eb91b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc930e4f4953f9a93a0c18eed0d9742ebab53c29","tid":1989451,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d33749588f2a7c40de23528ed2b632ec0cee62","tid":1989451,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"草龜 拎去水塘附近多草嘅地方"},{"pid":"bb91ef8a2e3eb0da603fcd083b018bd8beb7f7ff","tid":1989451,"uid":322836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔好放生，睇下龜group有冇人想養，放生等於殺死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613ff5715de25092b80370616753965f67b96ab5","tid":1989451,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"自己養埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f717964714ac2cc8441203fd577e694a2ff11c0","tid":1989451,"uid":213249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"相識也是緣份,有冇諗過養埋隻龜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70df39d8438fcd40c6b605c6d9cc7f17725a15ed","tid":1989451,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb91ef8a2e3eb0da603fcd083b018bd8beb7f7ff","tid":1989451,"uid":322836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔好放生，睇下龜group有冇人想養，放生等於殺死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"我知我家附近 有個水塘 周圍都好多草<br />\n我估佢應該係嗰度爬出黎 盪失路走左上馬路<br />\n之後就比我老母執左<br />\n<br />\n應該擺返本身既地方好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25afbb3f3cdb810911972ca171d857fd35000804","tid":1989451,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"養埋啦<br />\n風水龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990d2b7894cdef26d8e642f85b64885f20fe0b5a","tid":1989451,"uid":56188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"龜=壽徵=受精<br />\n恭喜包打就快多個細佬/妹"},{"pid":"6f95b482e860b1dfdd997e5072e988944d13f3fa","tid":1989451,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f717964714ac2cc8441203fd577e694a2ff11c0","tid":1989451,"uid":213249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"相識也是緣份,有冇諗過養埋隻龜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n龜都幾有靈性"},{"pid":"85b48b8e42fa107ed825fc5de763dd1bbe9be4b3","tid":1989451,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:06:41.000Z","msg":"龜易養？ 我驚我老母養死佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86356c3f867cecf403d674c90da0b78c4178c14","tid":1989451,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"救左隻佢係好事<br />\n但係放生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...?"},{"pid":"de712db763ad7e8860a601bea442bfb8d926cb92","tid":1989451,"uid":109355,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"巴西龜，水龜嚟，要喺水入面先食到嘢。放高啲水，有魚糧嗰啲可以餵小小，睇佢肯唔肯開口食嘢。"},{"pid":"3901ab6748185b9459a9c46c20c4fe9ec1d0f396","tid":1989451,"uid":185126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"放生？你弱智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044c96462a05c02f1664fdedd9c2bbcaa0d016c4","tid":1989451,"uid":252320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de712db763ad7e8860a601bea442bfb8d926cb92","tid":1989451,"uid":109355,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"巴西龜，水龜嚟，要喺水入面先食到嘢。放高啲水，有魚糧嗰啲可以餵小小，睇佢肯唔肯開口食嘢。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"巴乜鳩西乜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb7caf4ef0fb33c4c6bdfbd18586190a5ab8db5","tid":1989451,"uid":293244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"呢隻唔係草龜，係黃肚龜來,係來自北美洲的水龜。<br />\n<br />\n好似樓上有位巴打話齋唔好放生，佢地好似巴西龜咁適應力同競爭力強會破壞本地生態平衡。所以一係去養龜gp送出去一係自養啦。<br />\n<br />\n佢雜食性唔可以只喂菜。如果想自養就點都要有龜糧。間中餵下肉都ok。"},{"pid":"620135c51b5a1b5e061335cf35890a0c7bc4562f","tid":1989451,"uid":293244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"睇睇下都唔一定係黃肚 <br />\n<br />\n樓主可唔可以影多幾張相？例如佢個頭兩側的紋同底甲 咁會易d分辨出係咩品種 只睇背甲都唔太準"},{"pid":"4aa860948067b47634194d09d4baed68539bea13","tid":1989451,"uid":322836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3901ab6748185b9459a9c46c20c4fe9ec1d0f396","tid":1989451,"uid":185126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"放生？你弱智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:58:09.000Z","msg":"咁你又唔好咁鬧樓主，佢屋企人喺馬路見到隻龜都暫時執翻屋企，都已經好有善心，有咩唔明就問，唔洗咁鬧人哋弱智<br />\n至少佢都唔會話將隻龜放生喺大海<br />\n嗰啲先係有問題<br />\n想勸人嘅話，唔係你依啲態度"},{"pid":"7d31217573b2702efcba1de50ce594c2320bb4c4","tid":1989451,"uid":322836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70df39d8438fcd40c6b605c6d9cc7f17725a15ed","tid":1989451,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb91ef8a2e3eb0da603fcd083b018bd8beb7f7ff","tid":1989451,"uid":322836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔好放生，睇下龜group有冇人想養，放生等於殺死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"我知我家附近 有個水塘 周圍都好多草<br />\n我估佢應該係嗰度爬出黎 盪失路走左上馬路<br />\n之後就比我老母執左<br />\n<br />\n應該擺返本身既地方好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"我揸唔到主意啦，不過我都係偏向俾龜group人養，因為都未必肯定係水塘龜，最驚俾人棄養，茂茂言放喺水塘驚佢適應唔到，但俾佢哋養嘅話至少佢個居住環境安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02aec971f6bb46d225d4f4713510f0916b09a260","tid":1989451,"uid":109355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"044c96462a05c02f1664fdedd9c2bbcaa0d016c4","tid":1989451,"uid":252320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de712db763ad7e8860a601bea442bfb8d926cb92","tid":1989451,"uid":109355,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"巴西龜，水龜嚟，要喺水入面先食到嘢。放高啲水，有魚糧嗰啲可以餵小小，睇佢肯唔肯開口食嘢。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"巴乜鳩西乜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:06:31.000Z","msg":"咁你又知喺乜鳩龜吖？我錯你笑9我無問題，屌你日日食屎嚟，把口咁撚柒臭。"},{"pid":"8539d4149d824401958c49faa58c539bfe4a9c75","tid":1989451,"uid":252320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02aec971f6bb46d225d4f4713510f0916b09a260","tid":1989451,"uid":109355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"044c96462a05c02f1664fdedd9c2bbcaa0d016c4","tid":1989451,"uid":252320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de712db763ad7e8860a601bea442bfb8d926cb92","tid"